  <ResearchObelisk_BeamSplitter.ProjTypeLabel>升級組件</ResearchObelisk_BeamSplitter.ProjTypeLabel>
  <!-- EN: The Obelisks laser can be split using a beam splitter, the secondary beam is tuned to a particular wavelength and polarization state which disables personal shields, the primary beam is delayed by a fraction of a second and then delivered with full power to the target -->
  <ResearchObelisk_BeamSplitter.ResearchDesc>光明石碑可以使用電子束分裂器對激光進行分光處理，次級光束被調諧到特定的波長和極化狀態，用於擊破護盾，主光束延遲一秒到達，攻擊已無護盾保護的目標。</ResearchObelisk_BeamSplitter.ResearchDesc>
  <!-- EN: You can now produce Beam splitters's at the Rimatomics machining table, to install them into an Obelisk, select the Obelisk and designate the Beam splitter for installation -->
  <ResearchObelisk_BeamSplitter.ResearchDescDisc>您現在可以在「邊緣核能」加工台製作電子束分裂器，並將其安裝到光明石碑中，選擇光明石碑並指定安裝電子束分裂器。</ResearchObelisk_BeamSplitter.ResearchDescDisc>
  <!-- EN: Obelisk Beam Splitter -->
  <ResearchObelisk_BeamSplitter.ResearchLabel>電子束分裂器</ResearchObelisk_BeamSplitter.ResearchLabel>
